290
00:15:53,279 --> 00:15:56,519
Now it betrays my countless graces.

291
00:15:56,519 --> 00:16:00,600
Bones buried in green hills, soul shattered.

292
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:07,799
I'll burn through the heavens, destroy the gods.

293
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:16,120
Oh heavens!

294
00:16:18,480 --> 00:16:23,639
Oh heavens!

295
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:35,840
The morning dew shines,

296
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:47,200
