297
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:56,919
The moon before the cave flows, lighting all ages.

298
00:16:59,159 --> 00:17:02,919
I once thought this world was full of splendor.

299
00:17:02,919 --> 00:17:05,920
I once thought one could enjoy family bliss here.

300
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:09,240
Now the lamps dim, the stars grow faint.

301
00:17:09,319 --> 00:17:13,759
Now my eyes blur, clarity is gone.

302
00:17:13,759 --> 00:17:17,039
This world's order is broken, its morals confused.

303
00:17:17,039 --> 00:17:20,640
This world makes it hard to harden my heart.

304
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:27,240
Enough! I'll steel my heart.

305
00:17:27,559 --> 00:17:34,279
To the nine heavens, to prove my devotion.

306
00:17:34,279 --> 00:17:37,039
Keep my true nature, ascend to the nine heavens.

307
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:44,079
To prove my devotion.

308
00:17:44,079 --> 00:17:53,559
To prove my devotion.

309
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:41,359
Good

310
00:18:41,359 --> 00:18:42,680
Good

311
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:44,599
Sis, sis, sis

312
00:18:45,079 --> 00:18:47,440
Shaanxi Opera star Yi Qin'e

313
00:18:47,440 --> 00:18:49,680
has become, since this award was established,

314
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:51,799
the youngest recipient ever

315
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:53,400
The success of this play

316
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:56,200
also shows the impact of Shaanxi Opera

317
00:18:56,519 --> 00:19:00,759
adding a brilliant chapter to Shaanxi Opera culture

318
00:19:01,559 --> 00:19:03,960
Everyone's enthusiasm is understandable

319
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:06,680
Qin'e's performance was wonderful

320
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:09,000
