322
00:19:11,519 --> 00:19:12,519
What is this thing of yours?

323
00:19:12,519 --> 00:19:13,720
This crummy photo

324
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:15,039
The color's so faded

325
00:19:15,039 --> 00:19:16,440
Get a new one next time, okay?

326
00:19:16,440 --> 00:19:17,519
Okay

327
00:19:18,119 --> 00:19:20,599
Don't push, don't push, don't, don't

328
00:19:27,559 --> 00:19:28,839
Ms. Yi Qin'e

329
00:19:28,839 --> 00:19:31,279
They say opera is like life, and life is like opera

330
00:19:31,279 --> 00:19:32,319
So I'd like to ask

331
00:19:32,319 --> 00:19:33,519
In The Fox Immortal's Tribulation,

332
00:19:33,519 --> 00:19:36,039
the critique and despair toward the world,

333
00:19:36,039 --> 00:19:38,799
