334
00:19:39,240 --> 00:19:41,319
Whether they do, I can't really say

335
00:19:41,319 --> 00:19:42,400
But when I'm performing

336
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:44,480
Listen, your sis speaks so well

337
00:19:45,039 --> 00:19:46,279
Quiet, I'm watching

338
00:19:46,759 --> 00:19:47,240
Come on, come on, come on

339
00:19:47,240 --> 00:19:48,400
Drink up, drink up, drink up, come on

340
00:19:48,839 --> 00:19:49,319
Uncle

341
00:19:49,839 --> 00:19:51,759
But thanks to this role,

342
00:19:51,759 --> 00:19:53,519
you won opera's highest honor

343
00:19:53,519 --> 00:19:55,359
Look at these guys, just drinking

344
00:19:55,359 --> 00:19:56,759
Not even watching the TV properly

345
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:57,799
Brother

346
00:19:58,559 --> 00:20:01,759
For an opera singer to reach Laidi's level,

347
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:04,720
that's about as top as it gets

348
00:20:05,720 --> 00:20:07,400
Whether it's the top or not, who knows

349
00:20:08,319 --> 00:20:10,720
The old greats like Jiusuihong and Wei Changsheng,

350
00:20:11,039 --> 00:20:12,200
were probably about the same

351
00:20:22,519 --> 00:20:23,119
Here, Uncle

352
00:20:23,720 --> 00:20:23,920
Dad

353
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:25,759
Mom, why are you taking their candy?

354
00:20:27,519 --> 00:20:28,720
