356
00:20:30,559 --> 00:20:32,039
You always have to nag

357
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:34,440
Those cheap candies aren't worth anything

358
00:20:34,720 --> 00:20:36,160
Eat the meat, eat the meat

359
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:37,680
What, am I embarrassing you?

360
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:39,039
That's better, that's better

361
00:20:39,559 --> 00:20:40,160
Have a skewer

362
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:41,200
All you do is eat

363
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:41,519
Eat

364
00:20:41,519 --> 00:20:42,079
No, I won't

365
00:20:47,720 --> 00:20:48,359
Dad, here

366
00:20:48,359 --> 00:20:48,680
Here

367
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:49,839
Come on, come on, come on

368
00:21:18,039 --> 00:21:18,880
Laidi.

369
00:21:19,839 --> 00:21:20,920
Can't sleep?

370
00:21:21,599 --> 00:21:23,200
Mom, you're still up?

371
00:21:25,319 --> 00:21:28,200
Your sister snores louder than your dad.

372
00:21:28,720 --> 00:21:30,759
How does Gao Wufu put up with it?

373
00:21:34,279 --> 00:21:35,079
Laidi.

374
00:21:37,359 --> 00:21:39,759
The life you're living now,

375
00:21:40,319 --> 00:21:42,839
I never dared to even imagine it.

376
00:21:44,599 --> 00:21:46,200
If this were ancient times,

377
00:21:46,839 --> 00:21:49,000
this would be a life fit for an empress.

378
00:21:50,799 --> 00:21:52,200
I never imagined it either.

379
00:21:53,039 --> 00:21:54,920
Your sister keeps complaining.

380
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:56,920
She says, back then, your Uncle

381
00:21:57,359 --> 00:21:59,359
