383
00:22:04,279 --> 00:22:06,160
She just doesn't understand.

384
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:09,480
Even if your Uncle had taken her instead,

385
00:22:10,559 --> 00:22:12,880
she'd never have made it like you have.

386
00:22:15,240 --> 00:22:17,400
The kind of life a person leads,

387
00:22:18,680 --> 00:22:19,640
it's all fate.

388
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:27,559
Laidi.

389
00:22:30,480 --> 00:22:31,640
But still,

390
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:34,400
your sister's had a hard time too.

391
00:22:34,920 --> 00:22:37,240
Last year, that herbal medicine business

392
00:22:37,759 --> 00:22:39,359
lost her a huge sum of money.

393
00:22:39,839 --> 00:22:41,720
Your sister's life right now

394
00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:43,279
is really tough.

395
00:22:44,400 --> 00:22:45,799
If you can help her out,

396
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:47,720
please lend her a hand.

397
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:51,680
And your brother,

398
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:54,480
he can't stand staying in Jiuyangou anymore.

399
00:22:55,000 --> 00:22:57,400
All day, he wants to come to you.

400
00:22:58,240 --> 00:22:59,680
I've held him back for years,

401
00:23:00,559 --> 00:23:01,680
but the way it looks,

402
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:03,200
I can't stop him anymore.

403
00:23:08,759 --> 00:23:10,920
We'll deal with your brother later.

404
00:23:11,880 --> 00:23:13,799
First, live your own life well.

405
00:23:17,880 --> 00:23:19,200
Once you're married,

406
00:23:20,039 --> 00:23:21,640
you must be diligent,

407
00:23:23,359 --> 00:23:24,440
and be considerate.

408
00:23:24,720 --> 00:23:27,279
Don't trouble Bingbing with everything.

409
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:31,079
Whether a household holds together

410
00:23:32,240 --> 00:23:34,160
