411
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:42,640
My child.

412
00:23:44,839 --> 00:23:45,720
Give me your hand.

413
00:23:57,839 --> 00:23:59,279
Every woman suffers.

414
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:02,319
Mom has nothing to give you.

415
00:24:04,039 --> 00:24:05,480
Mom only hopes that you,

416
00:24:07,279 --> 00:24:09,599
