417
00:24:32,119 --> 00:24:33,559
All right, all right.

418
00:24:35,359 --> 00:24:36,920
Everyone, quiet down, quiet down now.

419
00:24:37,519 --> 00:24:38,000
Bing, dear,

420
00:24:38,319 --> 00:24:39,519
give your dad and mom

421
00:24:39,519 --> 00:24:40,640
