424
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:48,519
Good.

425
00:24:49,839 --> 00:24:50,799
Good.

426
00:24:54,160 --> 00:24:55,880
Dad, Mom,

427
00:24:56,440 --> 00:24:59,000
