428
00:24:59,519 --> 00:25:00,480
Don't cry.

429
00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:02,480
No tears on a day like today.

430
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:05,559
Bing, say a few words.

431
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:09,160
Dad, Mom,

432
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:10,880
I'll take care of Qin'e from now on.

433
00:25:11,359 --> 00:25:12,160
You can rest assured.

434
00:25:12,160 --> 00:25:13,319
Good.

435
00:25:15,680 --> 00:25:16,480
Bing, dear,

436
00:25:16,519 --> 00:25:17,680
