438
00:25:18,960 --> 00:25:19,400
Let's go.

439
00:25:20,119 --> 00:25:20,920
Pick her up!

440
00:25:21,839 --> 00:25:23,599
Pick her up!

441
00:25:23,599 --> 00:25:24,160
Come on.

442
00:25:26,519 --> 00:25:27,680
Off we go!

443
00:27:35,839 --> 00:27:36,839
It's lovely, just lovely.

444
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:39,160
This bridal home is beautifully done.

445
00:27:39,160 --> 00:27:39,759
Nice work.

446
00:27:39,759 --> 00:27:40,519
Very nice.

447
00:27:42,079 --> 00:27:43,240
I've had a bit too much to drink today.

448
00:27:43,240 --> 00:27:44,160
I'll head back now.

449
00:27:44,160 --> 00:27:44,799
Alright then.

450
00:27:44,799 --> 00:27:45,440
Director, let me see you out.

451
00:27:45,799 --> 00:27:46,359
No, no.

452
00:27:46,359 --> 00:27:47,200
You don't need to see me off.

453
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:48,559
Let Qin'e walk me out.

454
00:27:49,279 --> 00:27:50,960
The bride, let me share in some of her joy.

455
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:51,480
Yes, yes, yes.

456
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:52,440
Qin'e, see him off. Come on.

457
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:54,000
Qin'e's family is seeing you off, there's much to say.

458
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:54,759
Talk, talk, talk.

459
00:27:54,759 --> 00:27:55,480
Just see him to downstairs.

460
00:27:56,839 --> 00:27:57,400
Stay close, be careful.

461
00:27:57,400 --> 00:27:57,960
Okay, okay.

462
00:27:58,160 --> 00:27:59,000
Qin'e, keep an eye on him.

463
00:27:59,599 --> 00:28:00,039
Okay.

464
00:28:00,039 --> 00:28:00,599
Take it slow.

465
00:28:03,599 --> 00:28:04,920
Finally, I can breathe easy.

466
00:28:05,720 --> 00:28:06,440
Qin'e.

467
00:28:07,240 --> 00:28:10,079
Today, I really must congratulate you.

468
00:28:10,720 --> 00:28:12,759
You've been with the troupe for three years now.

469
00:28:12,759 --> 00:28:13,920
In these three years,

470
00:28:13,920 --> 00:28:15,640
I've watched you with my own eyes

471
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:18,000
