472
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:20,519
I guarantee that in another three years,

473
00:28:20,920 --> 00:28:22,720
your future will still be boundless.

474
00:28:23,119 --> 00:28:24,079
Trust me on this.

475
00:28:25,319 --> 00:28:26,039
So,

476
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:28,160
there's something I want to talk to you about.

477
00:28:28,160 --> 00:28:29,359
Don't think I'm nagging, okay?

478
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:30,839
What I was thinking is...

479
00:28:30,839 --> 00:28:31,599
Director Shan.

480
00:28:32,160 --> 00:28:33,000
I know.

481
00:28:34,200 --> 00:28:35,920
I'm not planning to have a child for now.

482
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:38,359
I'll keep singing for the troupe for a few more years.

483
00:28:39,240 --> 00:28:40,240
That's wonderful.

484
00:28:40,240 --> 00:28:42,119
That, that puts my mind at ease.

485
00:28:43,839 --> 00:28:45,720
Reportedly, this gang has long used

486
00:28:45,720 --> 00:28:46,759
the guise of a TV station,

487
00:28:46,839 --> 00:28:48,880
hosting fake children's singing contests,

488
00:28:48,880 --> 00:28:49,920
moving through multiple provinces and cities.

489
00:28:49,920 --> 00:28:50,440
What's he talking about?

490
00:28:50,440 --> 00:28:52,240
They swindled registration and training fees,

491
00:28:52,240 --> 00:28:53,880
totaling over 300,000 yuan.

492
00:28:54,400 --> 00:28:57,279
The ringleader, surnamed Mi, was caught in Nanjing.

493
00:28:57,279 --> 00:28:58,559
The case is still under further investigation.

494
00:28:58,559 --> 00:28:59,440
The case is still under further investigation.

495
00:29:00,079 --> 00:29:01,359
As the general public's

496
00:29:01,359 --> 00:29:02,519
standard of living rises,

497
00:29:02,519 --> 00:29:02,799
as living standards rise,

498
00:29:02,799 --> 00:29:04,319
people's demand for cultural entertainment

499
00:29:04,319 --> 00:29:05,559
and children's education

500
00:29:05,559 --> 00:29:06,759
has also been gradually increasing.

501
00:29:06,759 --> 00:29:07,599
However,

502
00:29:07,599 --> 00:29:08,200
everyone must keep their eyes wide open

503
00:29:08,200 --> 00:29:08,680
Who's that?

504
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:09,519
to avoid falling into

505
00:29:09,519 --> 00:29:09,960
Mi Lan.

506
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:11,200
traps that cost both money and dignity.

507
00:29:13,119 --> 00:29:14,319
No, it can't be.

508
00:29:17,039 --> 00:29:18,720
I've seen plenty of leading roles.

509
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:21,160
And I've seen even more leading ladies.

510
00:29:21,799 --> 00:29:24,480
Life is short, and fate is unpredictable.

511
00:29:25,160 --> 00:29:26,880
Right now, you need to take

512
00:29:26,880 --> 00:29:28,279
what you can hold on to

513
00:29:28,279 --> 00:29:30,440
and grip it tightly in your own hands.

514
00:29:34,519 --> 00:29:35,960
Make the days ahead good ones.

515
00:29:37,359 --> 00:29:38,319
Don't see me off any further. Go back.

516
00:29:41,160 --> 00:29:41,839
Live well.

517
00:30:10,799 --> 00:30:13,240
Tonight should have been the happiest day

518
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:15,119
