527
00:31:18,720 --> 00:31:21,240
Look over here.

528
00:31:26,599 --> 00:31:27,440
I had this custom-made just for you.

529
00:31:28,240 --> 00:31:28,799
Do you like it?

530
00:31:32,279 --> 00:31:33,640
Why did you have this made?

531
00:31:34,119 --> 00:31:34,960
What a waste of money.

532
00:31:35,960 --> 00:31:37,319
How could this be a waste of money?

533
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:38,880
People say

534
00:31:39,119 --> 00:31:40,480
