537
00:31:46,440 --> 00:31:46,960
So,

538
00:31:46,960 --> 00:31:48,359
I'll start by gifting you Mu Guiying's costume.

539
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:52,519
Come.

540
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:53,480
Take a look.

541
00:32:11,799 --> 00:32:12,319
Later on,

542
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:14,160
once we save up some money,

543
00:32:15,079 --> 00:32:16,119
I'll get you a full set

544
00:32:16,799 --> 00:32:17,880
