545
00:32:18,960 --> 00:32:19,480
Yang Paifeng's,

546
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:20,680
Bai Yunxian's,

547
00:32:21,759 --> 00:32:22,200
whatever you perform,

548
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:24,160
I'll get it for you.

549
00:32:44,759 --> 00:32:45,839
During those days,

550
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:48,480
Yi Qin'e was truly happy.

551
00:32:49,279 --> 00:32:50,640
Marriage was so wonderful

552
00:32:50,839 --> 00:32:52,039
that she didn't even notice

553
00:32:52,559 --> 00:32:53,640
the world outside

554
00:32:53,799 --> 00:32:55,160
had already been turned upside down.

555
00:32:56,279 --> 00:32:58,799
Trendy new things came flooding in.

556
00:32:59,519 --> 00:33:02,039
The thousand-year-old Shaanxi Opera,

557
00:33:02,519 --> 00:33:02,920
