563
00:33:19,000 --> 00:33:21,359
But she was still lost in her honeymoon.

564
00:33:22,119 --> 00:33:24,359
Fate doesn't care if you've woken up.

565
00:33:24,559 --> 00:33:26,640
The child came without warning.

566
00:33:27,319 --> 00:33:29,279
The trials meant for Yi Qin'e

567
00:33:29,279 --> 00:33:31,240
were only just beginning.

568
00:33:49,599 --> 00:33:51,480
Why give him water? What good is that?

569
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:52,680
Just feed him milk.

570
00:33:53,039 --> 00:33:54,480
The book says

571
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:56,440
you shouldn't soothe a crying baby with milk.

572
00:33:56,880 --> 00:33:58,160
He'll get dependent on it.

573
00:33:58,680 --> 00:34:01,240
Who raises a kid by the book? Come on.

574
00:34:01,240 --> 00:34:01,920
The baby's so little,

575
00:34:01,920 --> 00:34:03,119
why would you want to leave him?

576
00:34:03,519 --> 00:34:04,519
What kind of mother is that?

577
00:34:04,519 --> 00:34:05,200
Come, come, come.

578
00:34:05,640 --> 00:34:06,799
What kind of mom are you?

579
00:34:06,799 --> 00:34:08,119
Can't even soothe your own child.

580
00:34:08,119 --> 00:34:08,840
Come, come, come.

581
00:34:09,639 --> 00:34:10,360
Come, come, come.

582
00:34:11,159 --> 00:34:12,639
Don't cry, baby, don't cry.

583
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:18,079
My baby doesn't cry.

584
00:34:18,079 --> 00:34:19,639
Why is his face so red?

585
00:34:20,559 --> 00:34:21,559
The book says

586
00:34:21,559 --> 00:34:23,440
a red face is something to watch out for.

587
00:34:23,440 --> 00:34:25,039
Quit reading that lousy book.

588
00:34:26,119 --> 00:34:27,320
He's crying so hard,

589
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:28,599
of course his face is red.

590
00:34:29,639 --> 00:34:31,440
The moment you're born,

591
00:34:31,440 --> 00:34:32,880
life means suffering.

592
00:34:36,280 --> 00:34:38,079
Don't cry. Come, come.

593
00:34:40,519 --> 00:34:42,880
The baby wore everyone down to exhaustion.

594
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:46,480
And amid the endless crying

595
00:34:46,480 --> 00:34:48,519
and the tedium of housework,

596
00:34:48,840 --> 00:34:50,440
the marriage quietly began to crack.

597
00:34:52,039 --> 00:34:53,159
Laidi.

598
00:34:53,360 --> 00:34:55,599
Look, you're on TV.

599
00:34:56,000 --> 00:34:58,280
What opera is this?

600
00:34:59,719 --> 00:35:01,239
Look how pretty your mom is.

601
00:35:02,119 --> 00:35:03,679
She sings really well, though.

602
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:06,239
Director Shan.

603
00:35:07,639 --> 00:35:08,199
Sanyuan.

604
00:35:08,559 --> 00:35:09,519
I was just looking for you.

605
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:10,360
What is it?

606
00:35:11,239 --> 00:35:12,360
How's Qin'e doing these days?

607
00:35:13,199 --> 00:35:14,320
Same as ever.

608
00:35:14,920 --> 00:35:16,079
Home taking care of the baby.

609
00:35:16,079 --> 00:35:17,280
The kid's small, hard to manage.

610
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:19,760
The whole family looks like pandas.

611
00:35:19,760 --> 00:35:21,280
Look at those dark circles under their eyes.

612
00:35:21,559 --> 00:35:23,719
Why did she have a baby so early?

613
00:35:23,719 --> 00:35:25,159
Right after she got married,

614
00:35:25,159 --> 00:35:26,519
downstairs at her place,

615
00:35:26,519 --> 00:35:28,119
I told her loud and clear,

616
00:35:28,119 --> 00:35:29,920
"Wait a while, wait a while."

617
00:35:30,239 --> 00:35:31,119
What was she even thinking?

618
00:35:31,119 --> 00:35:32,599
Why have a baby so early?

619
00:35:35,440 --> 00:35:36,599
She never told me a thing.

620
00:35:36,599 --> 00:35:38,559
Well, that's just how she is.

621
00:35:39,039 --> 00:35:40,559
Keeps everything to herself.

622
00:35:40,559 --> 00:35:41,760
Doesn't tell anyone anything.

623
00:35:42,239 --> 00:35:44,039
She's got a mind of her own.

624
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:45,000
Look,

625
00:35:45,320 --> 00:35:46,639
right at her peak,

626
00:35:46,639 --> 00:35:47,840
she pulled out at the height of it all.

627
00:35:49,360 --> 00:35:50,599
Well, that's just her fate.

628
00:35:51,519 --> 00:35:53,039
She caught the golden age of Shaanxi Opera

629
00:35:53,239 --> 00:35:55,000
and missed its decline.

630
00:35:55,519 --> 00:35:57,280
After we performed The Fox Immortal's Tribulation

631
00:35:57,280 --> 00:35:58,679
those last few shows down south,

632
00:35:58,679 --> 00:35:59,719
once we got back,

633
00:35:59,719 --> 00:36:01,199
the troupe just fell apart.

634
00:36:01,719 --> 00:36:03,719
Everyone saw with their own eyes

635
00:36:03,719 --> 00:36:04,840
how prosperous the south is.

636
00:36:04,840 --> 00:36:06,559
They wonder what they've been doing all these years.

637
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:08,440
Everyone's heart is in chaos.

638
00:36:08,760 --> 00:36:10,480
I don't even know what to do anymore.

639
00:36:10,800 --> 00:36:12,599
Isn't there some new term now?

640
00:36:12,599 --> 00:36:14,960
They call Shaanxi Opera traditional folk culture.

641
00:36:15,239 --> 00:36:16,719
So maybe things will get better?

642
00:36:17,199 --> 00:36:18,159
I don't care about later.

643
00:36:18,159 --> 00:36:19,280
I only care about right now.

644
00:36:19,719 --> 00:36:20,920
There's one thing right now,

645
00:36:21,199 --> 00:36:23,039
you've got to get Qin'e back here for me.

646
00:36:23,039 --> 00:36:24,599
If she doesn't come back to sing,

647
00:36:24,599 --> 00:36:25,679
Shaanxi Opera is finished.

648
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:28,639
I'll go talk to her.

649
00:36:29,119 --> 00:36:29,960
I'll go talk to her.

650
00:36:35,239 --> 00:36:36,079
What for?

651
00:36:36,639 --> 00:36:37,480
I don't want it.

652
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:40,519
The troupe still pays 30% of my salary.

653
00:36:40,519 --> 00:36:41,360
I won't starve.

654
00:36:41,760 --> 00:36:42,800
This is a deposit.

655
00:36:44,679 --> 00:36:46,280
The troupe took on another show.

656
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:49,039
For the provincial Guanzhong Trade Fair.

657
00:36:49,960 --> 00:36:51,880
A proper performance, and the pay is good.

658
00:36:52,199 --> 00:36:53,079
500 per show.

659
00:36:53,519 --> 00:36:54,760
Star performers get extra on top.

660
00:36:55,280 --> 00:36:56,119
I can't go.

661
00:36:56,480 --> 00:36:57,000
Why not?

662
00:36:57,920 --> 00:36:59,440
The baby hasn't been weaned yet.

663
00:36:59,719 --> 00:37:01,360
Liu Hongbing's busy with work too.

664
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:01,960
If I leave,

665
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:04,079
my mom can't look after the kid alone.

666
00:37:04,800 --> 00:37:06,159
Just bring the kid along.

667
00:37:07,159 --> 00:37:09,360
The fans have missed you for so long.

668
00:37:10,039 --> 00:37:11,360
Then there's even less reason to go.

669
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:13,880
The way I am now,

670
00:37:15,440 --> 00:37:17,320
better to let them remember the old me.

671
00:37:19,760 --> 00:37:20,719
Think it over yourself.

672
00:37:22,119 --> 00:37:23,280
There's still a few days before we go.

673
00:37:23,599 --> 00:37:24,920
You decide whether to go or not.

674
00:37:40,159 --> 00:37:40,880
Comrades

675
00:37:42,320 --> 00:37:44,039
In over a decade of Reform and Opening Up,

676
00:37:45,159 --> 00:37:46,599
our Beishan region

677
00:37:46,599 --> 00:37:48,480
has made epoch-making progress.

678
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:50,760
Back in 1978,

679
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:53,639
our county GDP was just over 10 million yuan.

680
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:56,960
By last year, it broke through 100 million.

681
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:59,840
This year will be one of unity and progress,

682
00:38:00,239 --> 00:38:01,840
a year of leaps and bounds.

683
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:02,280
Bravo!

684
00:38:02,280 --> 00:38:03,079
Bravo!

685
00:38:03,079 --> 00:38:03,760
Bravo!

686
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:05,400
Stand up, stand up!

687
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:06,280
Stand up, stand up!

688
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:07,079
Come on, come on!

689
00:38:07,079 --> 00:38:08,199
Everyone stand up, stand up!

690
00:38:08,599 --> 00:38:09,639
Shout out the slogans!

691
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:10,480
Hongbing,

692
00:38:10,880 --> 00:38:13,119
aren't these slogans a bit over the top?

693
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:14,880
If you don't go big,

694
00:38:14,880 --> 00:38:16,280
how can you get his attention?

695
00:38:16,880 --> 00:38:18,239
You're just making snide remarks,

696
00:38:18,239 --> 00:38:19,280
all day long.

697
00:38:19,599 --> 00:38:20,880
Come, let's practice together.

698
00:38:20,960 --> 00:38:22,880
United as one!

699
00:38:22,880 --> 00:38:23,239
Liu Hongbing!

700
00:38:23,239 --> 00:38:23,679
Unity!

701
00:38:24,639 --> 00:38:25,639
What are you doing?

702
00:38:27,119 --> 00:38:28,320
Everyone, listen to me.

703
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:28,800
Let me say a few words, all right?

704
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:29,840
Let me say a few words, all right?

705
00:38:30,599 --> 00:38:31,400
The administrative division of our Beishan

706
00:38:31,400 --> 00:38:32,960
region has been changed.

707
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:35,119
From now on, it'll all be

708
00:38:35,119 --> 00:38:35,760
under Qinchuan's administration.

709
00:38:36,159 --> 00:38:38,960
Our office will also be downsized.

710
00:38:38,960 --> 00:38:39,079
This isn't something anyone

711
00:38:39,079 --> 00:38:41,400
just decided on a whim.

712
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:42,599
So,

713
00:38:42,599 --> 00:38:43,920
please, everyone, try to understand.

714
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:44,440
All right?

715
00:38:44,440 --> 00:38:45,039
Be understanding.

716
00:38:45,039 --> 00:38:46,159
Then what about us?

717
00:38:46,159 --> 00:38:47,239
We've got to eat, you know!

718
00:38:48,960 --> 00:38:49,960
Let me say a few words.

719
00:38:50,599 --> 00:38:51,639
You're downsizing,

720
00:38:52,239 --> 00:38:53,320
so what about all of us?

721
00:38:53,880 --> 00:38:55,679
We all need to put food on the table!

722
00:38:55,679 --> 00:38:56,000
Right!

723
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:56,480
Right!

724
00:38:56,480 --> 00:38:56,920
Yeah!

725
00:38:56,920 --> 00:38:58,800
Who said you couldn't eat?

726
00:38:59,920 --> 00:39:01,159
The leadership has given

727
00:39:01,159 --> 00:39:02,719
some thought to everyone's livelihood.

728
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:04,760
That's why funds were specially allocated

729
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:06,039
for buyouts based on years of service.

730
00:39:06,039 --> 00:39:07,719
Those with under 25 years of service

731
00:39:07,719 --> 00:39:08,599
get a flat subsidy of 10,000 yuan.

732
00:39:08,599 --> 00:39:09,079
A flat subsidy of 10,000 yuan.

733
00:39:09,079 --> 00:39:10,400
Those with 30 years of service

734
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:10,960
get a flat subsidy of 20,000 yuan.

735
00:39:10,960 --> 00:39:12,320
A flat subsidy of 20,000 yuan.

736
00:39:12,599 --> 00:39:13,599
Look, that's such a small sum.

737
00:39:13,599 --> 00:39:14,320
Liu Hongbing.

738
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:15,639
Liu Hongbing.

739
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:17,440
If you don't know what's good for you,

740
00:39:17,679 --> 00:39:18,320
fine,

741
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:19,840
go on leading everyone in making trouble.

742
00:39:20,840 --> 00:39:21,639
When the time comes,

743
00:39:21,639 --> 00:39:23,280
even this 10 or 20 grand will be gone.

744
00:39:23,280 --> 00:39:24,320
Let's see what you do then.

745
00:39:24,639 --> 00:39:26,000
They'll just carry on as usual.

746
00:39:26,519 --> 00:39:27,000
Just walking off like that?

747
00:39:27,000 --> 00:39:27,159
Just walking off like that?

748
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:30,400
Let me tell you all,

749
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:32,079
the tide of the times is coming,

750
00:39:32,639 --> 00:39:33,719
and no one can resist it.

751
00:39:35,239 --> 00:39:36,320
You can't just leave!

752
00:39:36,480 --> 00:39:37,960
You owe us an explanation!

753
00:39:40,199 --> 00:39:40,880
Hongbing.

754
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:42,119
What do we do, Hongbing?

755
00:39:42,119 --> 00:39:42,639
What are we gonna do?

756
00:39:42,639 --> 00:39:44,360
We'll all listen to you. What do we do?

757
00:39:44,360 --> 00:39:44,679
Tell us.

758
00:39:44,679 --> 00:39:45,719
What do we do now?

759
00:39:45,719 --> 00:39:47,400
Hongbing, come up with a plan for us.

760
00:39:47,400 --> 00:39:48,199
That's right, Hongbing.

761
00:39:48,199 --> 00:39:49,079
Say something!

762
00:39:52,800 --> 00:39:54,159
Planned economy

763
00:39:54,199 --> 00:39:55,760
Market economy

764
00:39:55,880 --> 00:39:57,199
Streamlining staff

765
00:39:57,239 --> 00:39:59,760
Layoffs, start over

766
00:40:00,400 --> 00:40:01,559
During that time

767
00:40:01,760 --> 00:40:03,320
The big headlines in the papers

768
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:04,719
The slogans on TV

769
00:40:04,920 --> 00:40:06,960
were repeated over and over

770
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:09,719
The tide of the era was coming

771
00:40:10,239 --> 00:40:12,039
No one could stand on the shore

772
00:40:12,320 --> 00:40:13,880
untouched by the waves

773
00:40:14,639 --> 00:40:15,800
Yi Qin'e knew

774
00:40:16,119 --> 00:40:18,480
everyone would be changed

775
00:40:23,440 --> 00:40:24,079
Sir

776
00:40:25,079 --> 00:40:26,119
Let's just stop fighting

777
00:40:26,119 --> 00:40:26,679
You go first

778
00:40:27,199 --> 00:40:27,639
Sorry

779
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:29,000
What's wrong with you?

780
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:05,880
Mom, Qin'e

781
00:41:06,920 --> 00:41:07,559
You're back

782
00:41:09,960 --> 00:41:10,599
Mom

783
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:12,079
The fish you wanted

784
00:41:14,960 --> 00:41:16,760
I told you to get crucian carp, crucian carp

785
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:17,840
This isn't crucian carp

786
00:41:17,840 --> 00:41:19,119
This one won't help with milk production

787
00:41:19,119 --> 00:41:20,320
Isn't that crucian carp?

788
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:21,760
The fishmonger said it was crucian carp

789
00:41:23,079 --> 00:41:24,000
It really isn't crucian carp

790
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:26,280
Let's just eat it first

791
00:41:26,280 --> 00:41:27,360
I'll buy her some tomorrow

792
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:31,880
The baby's out

793
00:41:32,719 --> 00:41:33,400
Come, let me hold him

794
00:41:33,400 --> 00:41:33,920
I just got him settled

795
00:41:33,920 --> 00:41:35,000
Don't make him cry again

796
00:41:35,719 --> 00:41:36,320
Okay

797
00:41:36,320 --> 00:41:38,280
Come, come, Daddy will hold you

798
00:41:39,559 --> 00:41:40,840
Daddy will hold you

799
00:41:42,280 --> 00:41:43,880
Can't even recognize crucian carp

800
00:41:45,280 --> 00:41:46,920
Truly born a rich young master

801
00:41:47,400 --> 00:41:48,719
Who am I raising this kid for?

802
00:41:49,239 --> 00:41:51,559
Played with Mommy all day, happy

803
00:41:53,559 --> 00:41:54,079
Qin'e

804
00:41:55,480 --> 00:41:57,239
Let's take the kid to the hospital tomorrow

805
00:41:57,239 --> 00:41:57,880
Check for what?

806
00:41:58,519 --> 00:41:59,400
I just feel like

807
00:41:59,800 --> 00:42:01,159
the kid seems a bit not normal

808
00:42:01,480 --> 00:42:02,960
What do you mean, not normal?

809
00:42:03,599 --> 00:42:04,400
He just cries a lot

810
00:42:04,400 --> 00:42:05,559
That makes him abnormal?

811
00:42:05,559 --> 00:42:06,840
You don't even talk to your dad

812
00:42:06,840 --> 00:42:07,880
You two aren't normal either

813
00:42:10,360 --> 00:42:11,400
Why are you arguing with me?

814
00:42:11,880 --> 00:42:12,719
What I mean is

815
00:42:12,719 --> 00:42:14,519
I feel like the kid's development is a bit slow

816
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:16,159
Compared to kids his age

817
00:42:16,480 --> 00:42:17,679
he can barely talk

818
00:42:17,679 --> 00:42:18,920
Who said anything?

819
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:21,679
My kid doesn't need to be compared with others

820
00:42:21,960 --> 00:42:23,320
Why do you care how others are?

821
00:42:23,920 --> 00:42:24,639
Fine, fine, fine

822
00:42:25,239 --> 00:42:27,239
If you think he's normal, he's normal

823
00:42:28,599 --> 00:42:29,480
Baby

824
00:42:30,000 --> 00:42:31,880
Listen to Mommy

825
00:42:32,159 --> 00:42:33,559
It's okay, it's okay

826
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:37,400
Listen to Mommy

827
00:42:37,400 --> 00:42:38,559
How's your workplace?

828
00:42:40,679 --> 00:42:41,199
What?

829
00:42:41,599 --> 00:42:42,840
How's your workplace?

830
00:42:43,760 --> 00:42:44,519
What about it?

831
00:42:45,119 --> 00:42:46,840
Aren't they doing layoffs?

832
00:42:49,960 --> 00:42:52,760
They'd never lay off Young Master Liu

833
00:42:53,960 --> 00:42:54,840
That's for the best

834
00:42:58,840 --> 00:42:59,239
What happened?

835
00:42:59,239 --> 00:42:59,800
Why did it burst?

836
00:43:09,679 --> 00:43:10,519
Chu Jiahe

837
00:43:11,000 --> 00:43:13,199
I'm telling you, I've done everything these years

838
00:43:13,559 --> 00:43:15,159
Can't help it, bad luck

839
00:43:15,400 --> 00:43:17,280
Didn't I have a stroke last year?

840
00:43:17,519 --> 00:43:19,000
Ended up like this

841
00:43:19,199 --> 00:43:19,599
Dad

842
00:43:21,159 --> 00:43:22,840
Uncle, I'm a bit nervous

843
00:43:22,920 --> 00:43:24,880
What big stages haven't we performed on?

844
00:43:24,880 --> 00:43:25,519
What's there to be nervous about?

845
00:43:26,079 --> 00:43:27,960
At weddings and funerals these days

846
00:43:28,320 --> 00:43:29,840
people want these new song-and-dance acts

847
00:43:30,280 --> 00:43:32,400
Who still watches the old Shaanxi Opera?
